Output assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Shell zsh

Type "cd ~/Desktop/CalibrCV/calibrcv-cli"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "node bin/calibrcv.js score ~/Desktop/Cagan_Oflazoglu_Resume.pdf"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
Sleep 3s
